  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "To the audience of Mr. Vajira",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "UNP Chairman Mr. Vajira Abeywardena has been appointed for the position of National List MP belonging to the United National Party.",
        "After Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe assumed the office of President, the position of National List MP held by the UNP became vacant.",
        "UNP General Secretary Palitha Ranga Bandara said that Mr. Vajira Abeywardena's name has been proposed for the post of National List Member of Parliament and the Election Commission has been informed about it."
      ],
